# Personal / Machine-Local Overrides (DO NOT COMMIT)

Copy this file to `CLAUDE.local.md` and fill in your local context. The `.local.md` version is gitignored.

## API Key References

API keys themselves live in environment variables (`.env`), never in this file. This file only documents WHICH keys are available.

- `TIINGO_API_KEY` — market data
- `FRED_API_KEY` — economic indicators
- `OPENAI_API_KEY` — embeddings for research notes (optional)

## Personal Preferences

- Preferred backtest universe: <e.g. S&P 500, Russell 1000>
- Default risk profile: <e.g. moderate, 15% vol target>
- Favorite chart library: <plotly, matplotlib, etc.>

## Local Data Paths

- Market data lake: `~/data/market/`
- Backtest results cache: `~/data/backtests/`
